{"tid":2151314,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"古惑仔肥屍：食黃店可以成為生活習慣 用twitter 都一樣可以！","createTime":"2020-08-11T10:26:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T01:02:24.000Z","uid":57328,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3b701bf683dc984b0c600209dedf17733b306742","tid":2151314,"uid":57328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:26:02.000Z","msg":"Twitter 唔單止係retweet任務，仲可以用黎了解世界各地唔同重要人物既即時意見，等於你自己做埋沈旭暉，第一時間知外國政要對香港有咩意見。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bergYCt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbergYCt.jpg&h=104b07eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你開一個ac, 跟小白鼠先生佢個list follow d 人已經好多野睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/shiroihamusan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fshiroihamusan&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9Fv1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=cf35766e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/shiroihamusan</a><br />\n<br />\n你唔使公開你個ac, 你幫手retweet post已經可以將啲新聞推上熱門<br />\n<br />\n進階版玩法 係follow 埋唔同國家既政要，作用係將香港既情況俾更加多國家既人知道，減低回音牆效應，即係你係fb like 啲page 既post 得自己香港人睇到咁樣，你可以由以下開始：<br />\n<br />\n加拿大～鄭敬基<br />\n美國～solomon<br />\n英國～牙聰<br />\n德國～呀ray<br />\n日本～葉錦龍，區諾軒等等<br />\n<br />\n你自己睇freeAgnes 個hastag 既hit<br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/hashtag/freeagnes?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&amp;src=hash\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fhashtag%2Ffreeagnes%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%26src%3Dhash&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9Fv1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=c1d36539\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/hashtag/freeagnes?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&amp;src=hash</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家你地問心，食黃店已經成為大家既日常生活習慣，咁所以用twitter 都可以成為習慣！<br />\n<br />\n用你上fb, tg 既時間抽啲出黎做下retweet 就可以，好過癮，唔單止淨係做任務咁簡單，學到好多野。"},{"pid":"357e94ed9f59837d2b0dab383a5bb8baff9e9da2","tid":2151314,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:30:04.000Z","msg":"用緊gab